						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Jaṭilavarman Tribhuvana-chakravartti Śaka 1472 Kōnēriṉmaikaṇḍāṉ Perumāḷ Kulaśēkharadēva.</hi></p>						

						<p>The record is dated in the Śaka year 1472 which along with other details of date <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> Piṅgaḷa, Paṅguṉi 15 ba 7, Wednesday and Viśakhanakshatra.</p>						

						<p>It records the grant of lands at Karivaranallūr in Āri-nāḍu as <hi rend="italic">kāṇiāṭchai</hi> in the name of Ativīrarāmaṉ.</p>						

						</summary>
